thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Ross & Daniela

author: Ross & Daniela
title: Ross & Daniela
text: We have been very happy with the service. Spiros has been professional in helping us find tenants. He worked hard and found the right people to rent our property and he did this within a week. Would highly recommend Spiro for anyone who is wanting to buy, sell or rent.
